			"relativePublishTimeDescription": "год назад",
			"rating": 1,
			"text": {
				"text": "This is literally the WORST clinic I've been to in Podgorica. They answer fast, but this is literally their only advantage. Doctors are totally uninterested in patients, interventions are painful, you are not given any anesthesia, and when you come for the second appointment you are told the nurse or the doctor is not here, and you have to wait at least an hour or probably more! Never go here if you have a choice.",
				"languageCode": "en"
			},
			"originalText": {
